DTEND;TZID=Europe/Moscow:20260710T103000
RRULE:FREQ=MONTHLY;BYMONTHDAY=10
SUMMARY:HEYS RKN change check
DESCRIPTION:Check whether last month changed PDN purpose category recipient system cross-border transfer or operator data. If changed prepare updateform before the 15th.
